  "Alexander Valley Homestead Red|Shrimp Cocktail": "Sonoma Bordeaux blend against cold raw shrimp with horseradish — red wine and chilled shellfish with cocktail sauce is textbook clash. Never pair. Route shrimp cocktail to Chardonnay, Sauvignon Blanc, Rosé, or Champagne; keep Homestead Red for the steak course.",
