  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Caymus Cabernet Sauvignon": "Caymus brings cocoa, mocha, velvety tannins — meets our manchego-baked potatoes squarely. The 90-minute bake caramelizes the cream and cheese; Caymus wraps around the richness. Peak Napa Cab pour for this side.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Château Batailley": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
