  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Cognac / Brandy": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this cognac's grape-distilled elegance with vanilla, dried fruit, and oak. Aged rum or cognac's sweetness and oak mirror the side's dairy-umami weight. Works cleanly.",
