  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Double-Oaked Bourbon": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this finished bourbon's wine-influenced sweetness and extra layer of complexity. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Works cleanly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Epoch Ingenuity": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Exotic-Cask Finished Bourbon": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this finished bourbon's wine-influenced sweetness and extra layer of complexity. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Works cleanly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Extra Añejo Tequila": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this añejo tequila's extended oak, vanilla, and caramel smoothness. Aged agave's warmth mirrors the side's richness. Works cleanly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Far Niente Cabernet Sauvignon": "Oakville Napa Cab — blackcurrant, dark chocolate, espresso, violet, smooth powerful. Lush and luxurious; handles the manchego gratin's 90-minute-baked richness with room to spare. Peak pour when the table's going big.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Far Niente Chardonnay": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this rich, oak-aged Chardonnay's butter, stone fruit, and full-bodied weight. Opulent Chardonnay's butter and oak mirror the side's dairy richness — same-register match. Works — a capable side pour.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Fattoria Le Pupille Saffredi": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Faust Napa Valley Cabernet": "Agustin Huneeus's elegant Napa Cab. Moderate tannin, fruit-forward. Works with the gratin but the bigger Cabs (Caymus, Far Niente) peak higher against the 90-minute-baked richness. Fine for a mid-tier Cab guest.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Filet Mignon": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets the filet's lean, buttery tenderness and delicate mineral edge. Classic steak-plus-side-or-soup pairing — weight, texture, and flavor fill the plate. Works — capable plate-builder.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Freemark Abbey Bosché": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Frias Block 5": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|G.D. Vajra Albe Nebbiolo": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Strong — the wine refreshes the side's richness.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|G.D. Vajra Moscato d'Asti": "Piedmont sweet sparkling — peach, honey, floral. The sweetness is catastrophic against a 180°C 90-minute-baked manchego cream gratin; the dish has too much savory weight and cream body. Route Moscato to dessert where sugar makes sense.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Ghost Block Cabernet Sauvignon": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Ghost Block Zinfandel": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Gundlach Bundschu Cabernet": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Head Fake": "Wheatley vodka, limoncello, triple sec, lemon, simple syrup, sugar rim. Sweet lemon-drop style clashes on every axis with manchego-cream gratin. Route this cocktail to dessert or to the lighter starters.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Heitz Martha's Vineyard": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Heitz Trailside Vineyard": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Highland Scotch": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this Highland Scotch's honey, heather, and light-fruit character on a medium body. Whiskey's vanilla and oak align with the side's dairy and umami depth. Works cleanly.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Inhibited": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this coffee-driven cocktail's bitter roast, rich texture, and dessert-adjacent sweetness. Coffee cocktail against a savory plate — wrong register entirely. Strong — the interaction lands despite the axis challenge.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|J. Davies Cabernet Sauvignon": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Strong — the wine refreshes the side's richness.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Jordan Cabernet Sauvignon": "Alexander Valley Cabernet — soft tannin. Cleaner Cab profile for our manchego gratin; handles the baked-cream richness without overwhelming the potato itself. Reliable Cab pour for a table splitting the gratin.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Jubilation by Colgin": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A capable pair; richness aligns if not perfectly.",
