  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Light / Wheated Bourbon": "Au Gratin Potatoes: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this wheated bourbon's approachable caramel, vanilla, and soft sweetness. Whiskey's vanilla and oak align with the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — aligned weight.",
  "Au Gratin Potatoes|Lingua Franca Avni Pinot Noir": "Willamette Pinot — low tannin, dark cherry, forest floor. The savory depth handles the manchego gratin's weight when the table's committed to Pinot; lighter red option alongside the richest potato.",
