  "Bone Marrow|Head Fake": "Bone Marrow: this rich, umami-forward starter's bold fat and concentrated savory depth meets this vodka cocktail's clean citrus lift and approachable sweetness. Light cocktail's citrus lift mirrors a delicate starter's brightness. Avoid.",
