  "Bone Marrow|Peanut Butter Brownie": "Same dense fudge base as our Chocolate Brownie, topped with whipped peanut butter frosting. Heavier finish than the chocolate version; viable if the guest is committed to peanut butter. Always flag peanut allergies before ordering.",
