  "Bowdie's Old Fashioned|Escargot": "Bowdie's Old Fashioned: this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth meets this rich, umami-forward starter's bold fat and concentrated savory depth. Whiskey depth meets the starter's fat and umami — both land heavy. Avoid.",
  "Bowdie's Old Fashioned|Evening Land Seven Springs": "Bowdie's Old Fashioned: this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth, considered as a bridge into this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. Avoid — the two drinks don't flow cleanly together.",
  "Bowdie's Old Fashioned|Far Niente Chardonnay": "Bowdie's Old Fashioned: this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth, considered as a bridge into this rich, oak-aged Chardonnay's butter, stone fruit, and full-bodied weight. Avoid — the two drinks don't flow cleanly together.",
