  "Bowdie's Old Fashioned|Filet Mignon": "Buffalo Trace, rum-soaked cherries, orange, bitters, large cube. Cocktail weight is heavier than the lean filet demands, but vanilla-caramel complements butter-tender beef and cherry sweetness bridges the mild profile. Strong when guest insists on spirit-forward alongside the most delicate cut.",
