  "Bowdie's Old Fashioned|Graham's 10 Year Tawny": "Bowdie's Old Fashioned: this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth, considered as a bridge into this tawny port's oxidative caramel, nut, and dried-fruit complexity. Avoid — the two drinks don't flow cleanly together.",
  "Bowdie's Old Fashioned|Graham's 20 Year Tawny": "Bowdie's Old Fashioned: this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth, considered as a bridge into this tawny port's oxidative caramel, nut, and dried-fruit complexity. Avoid — the two drinks don't flow cleanly together.",
  "Bowdie's Old Fashioned|Graham's 2017 Vintage Port": "Bowdie's Old Fashioned: this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth, considered as a bridge into this vintage port's dense dark fruit, structured tannin, and heady sweetness. Avoid — the two drinks don't flow cleanly together.",
