  "Brussels and Belly|Cowboy Ribeye": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this marbled ribeye's fatty richness, smoky crust, and bold beef expression. Classic steak-plus-side-or-soup pairing — weight, texture, and flavor fill the plate. Strong — balanced plate.",
  "Brussels and Belly|Craft / Blended Bourbon": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this bold, high-proof bourbon's oak spice, caramel weight, and heat. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "Brussels and Belly|Cucumber Gimlet": "Hendrick's muddled with cucumber, lime, ginger syrup, topped with soda. Cucumber-light cocktail for a pork-belly-forward side — the weights mismatch. Keep the Gimlet for lighter seafood; lean into Negroni or bourbon cocktails here.",
