  "Brussels and Belly|Espresso Martini": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this coffee-driven cocktail's bitter roast, rich texture, and dessert-adjacent sweetness. Coffee cocktail against a savory plate — wrong register entirely. Strong — the interaction lands despite the axis challenge.",
  "Brussels and Belly|Espresso Old Fashioned": "Buffalo Trace, Buffalo Bourbon Cream, Frangelico, espresso, brown sugar, Angostura. The coffee bitterness and Bourbon Cream pair with the lardons' cumin-and-smoked-paprika spice; brown sugar in both the cocktail and the lardon rub.",
  "Brussels and Belly|Evening Land Seven Springs": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Works — clean if not dominant.",
