  "Brussels and Belly|Head Fake": "Wheatley vodka, limoncello, triple sec, lemon, simple syrup, sugar rim. Sweet lemon-drop style clashes with cumin-smoked-paprika lardons; the rub's spice profile fights every component of the cocktail. Route to dessert.",
