  "Brussels and Belly|Highland Scotch": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this Highland Scotch's honey, heather, and light-fruit character on a medium body. Whiskey's vanilla and oak align with the side's dairy and umami depth. Works cleanly.",
