  "Brussels and Belly|Jordan Cabernet Sauvignon": "Alexander Valley Cabernet — elegant soft tannin, old-school Sonoma profile. Handles the pork-belly lardons' brown-sugar rub and the brussels' bitterness without overwhelming the side. Reliable Cab for a table splitting Brussels & Belly alongside steaks.",
