  "Brussels and Belly|Macauley Stagecoach Vineyard": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Brussels and Belly|Mezcal": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets the mezcal's smoky, earthy agave with distinctive mineral bite. Mezcal's smoke and earthy agave against the dish — smoke-meets-fat or smoke-meets-umami are the interesting axes. A headliner smoky-spirit pour.",
  "Brussels and Belly|Muga Reserva": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Brussels and Belly|Negroni": "Equal parts gin, Contratto vermouth, Campari. The Campari's bitter orange cuts through lardon fat and the Contratto's herbal depth plays against the cumin-paprika spice. Spirit-forward cocktail for a spirit-friendly side.",
  "Brussels and Belly|New York Sour": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Works cleanly.",
