  "Brussels and Belly|Not a Paper Plane": "Bulleit, Nonino amaro, Aperol, Angostura. Spirit-forward, stirred, bittersweet. The Nonino's herbal bitterness meets the brussels' vegetal bite, and the Aperol's orange hooks into the lardon's brown sugar rub. Non-obvious cocktail pairing that rewards attention.",
