  "Brussels and Belly|Silver Oak Cabernet Sauvignon": "American oak-aged Cabernet with softer tannin. The American-oak vanilla plays with our lardons' brown sugar and cumin-paprika rub; accessible peak pour for the shareable. Works for a table that wants a recognizable name over structured complexity.",
  "Brussels and Belly|Simon Family Estate Reserve": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
