  "Brussels and Belly|The Tomahawk": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this marbled ribeye's fatty richness, smoky crust, and bold beef expression. Classic steak-plus-side-or-soup pairing — weight, texture, and flavor fill the plate. Strong — balanced plate.",
