  "Burrata|Bee's Knees": "Empress Indigo gin with lemon and honey lavender syrup. The honey works seasonally with whatever fruit the kitchen has on the plate; the Indigo's butterfly-pea color-shift is a detail to mention alongside a vegetarian starter.",
  "Burrata|Blanco Tequila": "Burrata: the burrata's creamy, fresh dairy mildness meets this blanco tequila's bright, clean agave with citrus and pepper. The spirit functions as a palate-setter here rather than a true counterpart to the plate. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
