  "Burrata|Cucumber Gimlet": "Hendrick's muddled with cucumber, lime, ginger syrup, topped with soda. Cucumber-forward cocktail against creamy burrata — a fresh, clean move that doesn't fight the seasonal fruit or the balsamic glaze. The easiest cocktail on the menu to love.",
