  "Burrata|Elk Cove Pinot Blanc": "Oregon Pinot Blanc — pear and apple, clean acid. Fresh fruit against the creamy burrata and whatever seasonal fruit component the kitchen adds today. Reliable mid-tier white that always works with fresh cheese and fruit preparations.",
