  "Caymus Cabernet Sauvignon|Escargot": "Caymus Cabernet Sauvignon: this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight meets this rich, umami-forward starter's bold fat and concentrated savory depth. The bold red's tannin scrubs the starter's fat while dark fruit picks up the umami notes. Not the sharpest pairing.",
  "Caymus Cabernet Sauvignon|Faroe Island Salmon": "Caymus Cabernet Sauvignon: this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight meets this rich, fatty seafood's buttery flesh and delicate-yet-substantial texture. The bold red's tannin shreds the fish's delicate flake, and the dark fruit clashes with briny sweetness. Textbook avoid — this is the classic red-meat-only territory.",
  "Caymus Cabernet Sauvignon|Filet Mignon": "Caymus — Napa Rutherford Cab, concentrated black fruit, cocoa, mocha, velvety tannin. The opulent body meets butter-tender filet's lean sweetness and the cocoa-mocha echoes escargot-butter toppers. Peak iconic Napa Cab for filet — the name, the opulence, the long warming finish all line up for the classic cut.",
