  "Chocolate Brownie|Wine-Finished Bourbon": "Chocolate Brownie: this dense chocolate dessert's deep cocoa richness meets this finished bourbon's wine-influenced sweetness and extra layer of complexity. Bold whiskey meets rich chocolate — cross-category depth that plays. A headliner dessert pour.",
