  "Classic Vodka|Roast Half Chicken": "Classic Vodka: this vodka's neutral, clean profile with minimal influence meets this roasted chicken's savory, rich poultry-skin flavor. Spirit or liqueur alongside roasted chicken — depends on the spirit's depth. Works as a sideline pour.",
  "Classic Vodka|Seafood Tower": "Classic Vodka: this vodka's neutral, clean profile with minimal influence meets this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness. The spirit functions as a palate-setter here rather than a true counterpart to the plate. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "Classic Vodka|Seared Scallops": "Classic Vodka: this vodka's neutral, clean profile with minimal influence meets this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness. Neutral spirit profile means this reads as an opener, not a built pairing. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "Classic Vodka|Shrimp Bisque": "Classic Vodka: this vodka's neutral, clean profile with minimal influence meets this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base. Clean spirit against a rich soup — the drink reads thin against the weight. Strong — the interaction lands despite the axis challenge.",
