  "Crab Cake|Far Niente Chardonnay": "Crab Cake: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this rich, oak-aged Chardonnay's butter, stone fruit, and full-bodied weight. Oaky Chardonnay's weight against a starter — texture heavy if the plate is delicate. Strong when the starter is rich.",
  "Crab Cake|Fattoria Le Pupille Saffredi": "Crab Cake: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Delicate seafood or mild creams buckle under the bold red's tannin. Avoid — register mismatch.",
