  "Crab Cake|Fisher Unity Pinot Noir": "Crab Cake: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's silky frame sits alongside the starter without weight-fighting — the fruit threads through the plate. A headliner starter pair.",
