  "Crab Cake|G.D. Vajra Moscato d'Asti": "Crab Cake: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets the Moscato's peach-and-honey sweetness with delicate effervescence. Moscato's sweetness on a savory plate — wrong register. Strong when the dish plays sweet — not the default.",
