  "Creamed Spinach|Exotic-Cask Finished Bourbon": "Creamed Spinach: this rich, creamy side's dairy-driven indulgence meets this finished bourbon's wine-influenced sweetness and extra layer of complexity. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — richness aligned.",
