  "Grilled Caesar|Jean-Pierre Grossot Chablis": "Chablis Chardonnay — oyster-shell minerality, bright acid. Handles the dressing's richness and the anchovy base; textbook Caesar pairing. The mineral character also cuts through the grilled-romaine char without fighting it.",
