  "Grilled Caesar|Pineau des Charentes": "Grilled Caesar: the Grilled Caesar's charred romaine, anchovy umami, and bold creamy dressing meets the Pineau's grape-sweet, cognac-warmed aperitif profile. Dessert-register fortified meets savory food — the sweetness usually overruns the dish. Works as a transition from savory into dessert.",
