  "House Wedge|Sanford & Benedict Pinot Noir": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's cherry and light tannin mirror the wedge's crisp-creamy balance. Strong — same-register match.",
  "House Wedge|Sazerac": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth. Heavy whiskey on a crisp wedge — the drink steamrolls the salad. Works only as an aperitif alongside.",
  "House Wedge|Scavino Barolo": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The wedge's crisp iceberg and creamy dressing sit light against the bold red's dense tannin — the wine overwhelms the salad. Works only as a second-thought pairing.",
  "House Wedge|Schloss Vollrads Riesling": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this off-dry Riesling's stone-fruit sweetness and mineral backbone. Crisp acidity meets crisp lettuce — a clean, aligned pour. Strong — clean alignment.",
  "House Wedge|Scotto Cellars The Lost Chapters": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's cherry and light tannin mirror the wedge's crisp-creamy balance. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "House Wedge|Sesti Brunello di Montalcino": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The wedge's crisp iceberg and creamy dressing sit light against the bold red's dense tannin — the wine overwhelms the salad. Works only as a second-thought pairing.",
  "House Wedge|Shafer 1.5": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The wedge's crisp iceberg and creamy dressing sit light against the bold red's dense tannin — the wine overwhelms the salad. Works only as a second-thought pairing.",
  "House Wedge|Shafer Hillside Select": "Stag's Leap flagship Cabernet. Same problem as Opus — the blue cheese dressing flattens the structured tannin that makes this bottle worth pouring. Save for the steak course; don't waste the pour on salad.",
  "House Wedge|Silver Oak Cabernet Sauvignon": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The wedge's crisp iceberg and creamy dressing sit light against the bold red's dense tannin — the wine overwhelms the salad. Works only as a second-thought pairing.",
  "House Wedge|Simon Family Estate Reserve": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The wedge's crisp iceberg and creamy dressing sit light against the bold red's dense tannin — the wine overwhelms the salad. Works only as a second-thought pairing.",
  "House Wedge|Smooth / Citrus Craft Gin": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this contemporary gin's floral, fruit-forward botanical profile. Clean spirit against a crisp salad — the drink reads aperitif, not pairing. Strong — the interaction lands despite the axis challenge.",
  "House Wedge|Spiced / Flavored Rum": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this spiced rum's sweet, approachable warmth. Clean spirit against a crisp salad — the drink reads aperitif, not pairing. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "House Wedge|Spottswoode Lyndenhurst": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's cherry and light tannin mirror the wedge's crisp-creamy balance. Works as a plate-opener pour.",
  "House Wedge|St Supéry Cabernet Sauvignon": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's cherry and light tannin mirror the wedge's crisp-creamy balance. Works as a plate-opener pour.",
  "House Wedge|St Supéry Sauvignon Blanc": "Napa Sauvignon Blanc — grassy, citrus-forward. Bright acid handles the blue cheese weight and the grass note echoes the iceberg's freshness. Reliable California pivot for guests who want white with salad.",
  "House Wedge|St Supéry Élu Meritage": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The wedge's crisp iceberg and creamy dressing sit light against the bold red's dense tannin — the wine overwhelms the salad. Works only as a second-thought pairing.",
  "House Wedge|Standard High-Proof Bourbon": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this bold, high-proof bourbon's oak spice, caramel weight, and heat. Heavy whiskey on a crisp wedge — the drink steamrolls the salad. Works only as an aperitif alongside.",
  "House Wedge|Stoneleigh Sauvignon Blanc": "Marlborough Sauvignon Blanc — grassy, green, affordable. Bright entry point for blue cheese salads; does the same cutting work as our St Supéry at a lower price point. Good house-wedge pour for a first round.",
  "House Wedge|Teeter Totter Cabernet Sauvignon": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The wedge's crisp iceberg and creamy dressing sit light against the bold red's dense tannin — the wine overwhelms the salad. Works only as a second-thought pairing.",
  "House Wedge|Tenuta di Arceno Chianti Classico": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The wedge's crisp iceberg and creamy dressing sit light against the bold red's dense tannin — the wine overwhelms the salad. Works only as a second-thought pairing.",
  "House Wedge|The BG": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth. Heavy whiskey on a crisp wedge — the drink steamrolls the salad. Strong — the interaction lands despite the axis challenge.",
  "House Wedge|The Happy Wife": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this gin cocktail's citrus brightness and botanical lift. Light, bright cocktail matches the wedge's own lightness. Strong — aligned lift.",
  "House Wedge|The Manhattan": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth. Heavy whiskey on a crisp wedge — the drink steamrolls the salad. Works only as an aperitif alongside.",
