  "House Wedge|Transfusion": "House Wedge: the House Wedge's crisp iceberg against creamy bleu dressing meets this gin cocktail's citrus brightness and botanical lift. Light, bright cocktail matches the wedge's own lightness. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
