  "J. Davies Cabernet Sauvignon|Au Gratin Potatoes": "Diamond Mountain Cab — dark fruit, graphite, mineral backbone, firm tannin. The structured body cuts au gratin's cheese-and-cream weight and the graphite plays against the golden crust. Strong mountain Cab for au gratin — volcanic-soil complexity on the decadent side.",
