  "Jax Calesa Vineyard Pinot Noir|Filet Mignon": "Russian River Pinot — red cherry, pomegranate, subtle earth, balanced acidity, smooth finish, medium body. The smooth structure meets butter-tender filet's lean sweetness and the subtle earth plays against escargot-butter toppers. Peak food-friendly Pinot for filet — reliable Russian River on the delicate cut.",
