  "Joseph Mellot Sancerre|Vegetable Curry with Chickpeas": "Loire Sancerre — refined tension-filled mineral, citrus, flint. The flinty citrus tension cuts the curry's coconut-milk weight and the mineral plays against chickpea earth. Works as Sancerre for the curry — Loire precision on the spiced classic; Riesling peaks higher on the heat.",
  "Jubilation by Colgin|Au Gratin Potatoes": "Jubilation — Colgin cult Napa, blackcurrant, dark chocolate, violets, espresso, firm tannin. The firm tannin cuts gruyère-cream weight and the espresso plays against the lactic richness. Works as cult Napa for au gratin — Colgin prestige on the cheesy side.",
  "Jubilation by Colgin|Bone Marrow": "Jubilation — Colgin cult Napa, blackcurrant, dark chocolate, violets, espresso, firm tannin. The firm tannin cuts marrow's collagen fat and the espresso-chocolate plays against the smoky mineral depth. Peak cult Napa for marrow — Colgin prestige on the rich starter with reverence.",
