  "Lail Vineyards Daniel Cuvée|Kansas City": "Lail flagship multi-appellation Napa Cab — dark fruit, cassis, graphite, dried violet, firm tannin. The firm tannin meets Kansas City's lean-bold marbled strip and the graphite plays against beefy char. Strong historically-significant Napa Cab for the strip — Daniel Cuvée pedigree on the American cut.",
