  "Mushrooms|Clos Petit Ona Grenache": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. A bright-meets-rich headliner.",
  "Mushrooms|Cognac / Brandy": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this cognac's grape-distilled elegance with vanilla, dried fruit, and oak. Aged rum or cognac's sweetness and oak mirror the side's dairy-umami weight. Strong — aligned depth.",
  "Mushrooms|Corazón del Sol Malbec": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A headliner pair — pour confidently.",
  "Mushrooms|Craft / Blended Bourbon": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this bold, high-proof bourbon's oak spice, caramel weight, and heat. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — richness aligned.",
  "Mushrooms|Cristom Mt Jefferson Cuvée": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Strong — the wine refreshes the side's richness.",
  "Mushrooms|Daniel Chotard Sancerre Rouge": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Works — clean if not dominant.",
  "Mushrooms|Darioush Cabernet Franc": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A headliner pair — pour confidently.",
  "Mushrooms|Darioush Cabernet Sauvignon": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Mushrooms|Dark / Aged Rum": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this aged rum's molasses, vanilla, and caramel depth. Aged rum or cognac's sweetness and oak mirror the side's dairy-umami weight. Strong — aligned depth.",
  "Mushrooms|Domaine Serene Grand Cheval": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Strong — the wine refreshes the side's richness.",
