  "Mushrooms|Domaine du Grand Tinel": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A headliner pair — pour confidently.",
  "Mushrooms|Double-Oaked Bourbon": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this finished bourbon's wine-influenced sweetness and extra layer of complexity. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — richness aligned.",
  "Mushrooms|Elk Cove Five Mountain": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. Strong — the wine refreshes the side's richness.",
  "Mushrooms|Epoch Ingenuity": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A headliner pair — pour confidently.",
  "Mushrooms|Evening Land Seven Springs": "Eola-Amity Hills Pinot — black cherry, smoked meat, dried rose, crushed stone. The smoked-meat note meets mushroom umami directly; serious Willamette Pinot that doesn't back down from the earthy depth and rewards a guest seeking refinement alongside mushrooms.",
  "Mushrooms|Exotic-Cask Finished Bourbon": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this finished bourbon's wine-influenced sweetness and extra layer of complexity. Whiskey's oak and sweetness mirror the side's dairy and umami depth. Strong — richness aligned.",
  "Mushrooms|Extra Añejo Tequila": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this añejo tequila's extended oak, vanilla, and caramel smoothness. Aged agave's warmth mirrors the side's richness. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
  "Mushrooms|Far Niente Cabernet Sauvignon": "Oakville Napa Cab — blackcurrant, dark chocolate, espresso, violet, smooth powerful finish. The dark-chocolate-and-espresso notes meet mushroom umami directly; luxurious peak Cab pour for the earthy side when the guest wants top-shelf alongside their steak.",
  "Mushrooms|Fattoria Le Pupille Saffredi": "Strong tier. Sautéed Shiitakes, creminis, and oyster mushrooms in butter, shallots, garlic, and thyme meet the Saffredi's earthy graphite and Mediterranean herbs head-on. Maremma Super Tuscan tannin cuts the butter finish, while tobacco and blackcurrant pick up the thyme-butter depth.",
  "Mushrooms|Faust Napa Valley Cabernet": "Agustin Huneeus's elegant Napa Cab — moderate tannin, fruit-forward, polished finish. Works with mushrooms, but the bigger Cabs (Caymus, Far Niente, Opus) peak higher against the umami depth. Acceptable mid-tier Cab pour when price sensitivity matters.",
  "Mushrooms|Fento Ollo de Sapo Mencía": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. A bright-meets-rich headliner.",
  "Mushrooms|Filet Mignon": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets the filet's lean, buttery tenderness and delicate mineral edge. Classic steak-plus-side-or-soup pairing — weight, texture, and flavor fill the plate. Works — capable plate-builder.",
  "Mushrooms|Freemark Abbey Bosché": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Mushrooms|Frias Block 5": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Mushrooms|G.D. Vajra Albe Nebbiolo": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. The elegant red's acidity cuts the dairy fat while its cherry lifts the earthy umami. A bright-meets-rich headliner.",
  "Mushrooms|G.D. Vajra Moscato d'Asti": "Piedmont sweet sparkling — peach, honey, floral. Sweetness fights every umami aspect of the mushrooms; the earthy depth gets fought by every note in the wine. Route Moscato to dessert.",
  "Mushrooms|Ghost Block Cabernet Sauvignon": "Oakville Cabernet — firm structure, classic Napa profile with dust-and-dark-fruit character. That character meets mushroom umami directly; solid mid-tier Napa Cab pairing that holds up with the spirit-friendly side without Caymus or Far Niente-level weight.",
  "Mushrooms|Ghost Block Zinfandel": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
  "Mushrooms|Gundlach Bundschu Cabernet": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A headliner pair — pour confidently.",
  "Mushrooms|Head Fake": "Wheatley vodka, limoncello, triple sec, lemon, simple syrup, sugar rim. Sweet lemon-drop clashes on every axis with mushroom umami; the cocktail's profile fights the side. Route to dessert or lighter courses.",
  "Mushrooms|Heitz Martha's Vineyard": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A strong, texturally cohesive match.",
