  "Mushrooms|Highland Scotch": "Mushrooms: this earthy, umami-packed side's mushroom-and-truffle depth meets this Highland Scotch's honey, heather, and light-fruit character on a medium body. Whiskey's vanilla and oak align with the side's dairy and umami depth. A headliner match — context-driven peak.",
