  "Odette Cabernet Sauvignon|Au Gratin Potatoes": "Stags Leap Cab — dark fruit, sage, cedar, graphite, refined tannin. The velvet-glove body cuts au gratin's cheese-and-cream weight and the sage-cedar plays against the golden crust. Works as refined Stags Leap Cab for au gratin — iron-fist-velvet-glove balance on the decadent side.",
