  "Odette Cabernet Sauvignon|Cowboy Ribeye": "Stags Leap Cab — dark fruit, sage, cedar, graphite, firm refined tannin. The velvet-glove body handles Cowboy's marbled bone-in richness and the sage-cedar meets rendered fat. Strong refined Cab for Cowboy — iron-fist-velvet-glove balance, though Silver Oak, Caymus, or Frias peak higher for the fattiest ribeye.",
