  "Odette Cabernet Sauvignon|Creamed Spinach": "Odette — Stags Leap Cab with dark fruit, sage, cedar, graphite, refined tannin. The velvet-glove body cuts creamed spinach's dairy weight and the sage-cedar plays against the earthy sauce. Strong refined Stags Leap Cab for creamed spinach — iron-fist-velvet-glove balance on the classic side.",
  "Odette Cabernet Sauvignon|Filet Mignon": "Odette — Stags Leap Cab with iron-fist-in-a-velvet-glove quality. Dark fruit, sage, cedar, graphite, firm but remarkably refined tannin. The body meets butter-tender filet's lean sweetness and the sage-cedar echoes escargot-butter toppers. Peak refined Cab for filet — Stags Leap signature balance on the classic tenderloin cut.",
  "Odette Cabernet Sauvignon|Grilled Caesar": "Odette — Stags Leap Cab with dark fruit, sage, cedar, graphite. The velvet-glove body meets anchovy-parmesan dressing and the sage-cedar plays against grilled-romaine char. Works as refined Stags Leap Cab for grilled Caesar — iron-fist-velvet-glove balance on the classic layered salad.",
