  "Odette Cabernet Sauvignon|Kansas City": "Stags Leap Cab — dark fruit, sage, cedar, graphite, firm but refined tannin, velvet-glove balance. The structured body meets Kansas City's lean-bold marbled strip and the sage-cedar plays against the beefy char. Peak refined Cab for Kansas City — Stags Leap iron-fist-velvet-glove character on the classic strip.",
  "Odette Cabernet Sauvignon|Mushrooms": "Odette — Stags Leap Cab with dark fruit, sage, cedar, graphite, refined tannin. The sage-cedar-graphite meshes with mushroom umami and the velvet-glove body frames the sauté earth. Peak refined Stags Leap Cab for mushrooms — sage-on-earth match plus iron-fist-velvet-glove balance.",
