  "Opus One|Burrata": "Collector Napa Cab blend against burrata's creamy-delicate center — Opus One's firm-tannin Bordeaux-blend structure overwhelms the starter. Never pair. Route burrata to Chardonnay, Sauvignon Blanc, Rosé, or Prosecco; keep Opus One for the steak course.",
