  "Opus One|Crab Cake": "Collector Napa Cab blend against crab cake's delicate sweet meat — Opus One's firm-tannin Bordeaux blend buries the shellfish. Never pair. Route crab cake to Chardonnay, Sauvignon Blanc, Rosé, or Champagne; keep Opus One for the steak course.",
