  "Opus One|Creamed Spinach": "Opus One — Oakville Bordeaux blend, dark fruit, mocha, cedar, dried violet, firm tannin. The firm tannin cuts béchamel's dairy weight and the mocha plays against the spinach base. Strong collector Napa blend for creamed spinach — prestige wine reframes the rich steakhouse side.",
