  "Opus One|Grilled Caesar": "Opus One: this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight meets the Grilled Caesar's charred romaine, anchovy umami, and bold creamy dressing. Tannin and char, umami and dark fruit — the bold red and the Caesar punch at the same level. Avoid — the bold red overreaches.",
