  "Opus One|Honey Roasted Carrots": "Opus One: this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight meets these honey-roasted carrots' caramelized sweetness and earthy warmth. Bitter greens or sweet roots don't carry the tannin — the wine overruns the vegetable. Avoid — green and grassy flattens the bold red's fruit.",
