  "Scavino Barolo|The Tomahawk": "Piedmont Barolo DOCG Nebbiolo — Scavino Castiglione Falletto, tar, dried rose, cherry, leather, powerful firm tannin, high acid, full body. The powerful tannin handles Tomahawk's massive bone-in ribeye and the tar-leather plays against smoky char. Peak King-of-Italian for Tomahawk — Scavino prestige on the grand cut, demands the beef.",
