  "Scavino Barolo|Truffle Fries": "Piedmont Barolo DOCG Nebbiolo — Scavino Castiglione Falletto, tar, dried rose, cherry, leather, powerful firm tannin, high acid. The firm tannin cuts truffle-fry potato fat and the tar plays against the truffle-oil umami. Peak King-of-Italian for truffle fries — tar-truffle echo, Scavino prestige on the umami hit.",
