  "Seafood Tower|Cucumber Gimlet": "Hendrick's muddled with cucumber, lime, ginger syrup, topped with soda. Cucumber-light cocktail holds up against shellfish; ginger syrup adds a little depth that keeps it from being one-dimensional. Refreshing alongside the tower.",
  "Seafood Tower|Elk Cove Pinot Blanc": "Oregon Pinot Blanc — crisp pear and apple, clean acid. Safe pour for the table that's price-conscious or not into sparkling; handles oysters and shrimp without trouble. Not the peak, but never wrong.",
  "Seafood Tower|Espresso Martini": "Seafood Tower: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this coffee-driven cocktail's bitter roast, rich texture, and dessert-adjacent sweetness. Coffee cocktail against a savory plate — wrong register entirely. Avoid — save for dessert.",
  "Seafood Tower|Espresso Old Fashioned": "Seafood Tower: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this coffee-driven cocktail's bitter roast, rich texture, and dessert-adjacent sweetness. Coffee cocktail against a savory plate — wrong register entirely. Avoid — save for dessert.",
