  "Seared Scallops|Alexander Valley Homestead Red": "Seared Scallops: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this medium-bodied red's approachable fruit and food-friendly acidity. Cherry brightness and low tannin let the elegant red move with the starter instead of crowding it. Avoid.",
