  "Seared Scallops|Peated Islay Scotch": "Seared Scallops: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this Islay Scotch's intense peat smoke, medicinal phenol, and bold weight. Whiskey's oak and caramel are only going to land if the starter can carry weight — check the plate. Avoid — too heavy for delicate starters.",
