  "Shrimp Bisque|Macauley Pinot Noir": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's cherry and earth anchor into rich soup depth — acidity cuts the cream. Works — coherent if not a headliner.",
