  "Shrimp Bisque|New York Sour": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth. Cocktail against a creamy seafood soup — acidity and lift cut the dairy base while the spirit carries its own weight. Strong — bright cuts rich.",
