  "Shrimp Bisque|Pineau des Charentes": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets the Pineau's grape-sweet, cognac-warmed aperitif profile. Dessert-register fortified meets savory food — the sweetness usually overruns the dish. Works as a transition from savory into dessert.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|RAEN Royal St Robert": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's cherry and earth anchor into rich soup depth — acidity cuts the cream. Strong — bright fruit lifts the weight.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Raventós Cava de NIT Rosé Brut": "Rosé Cava — sparkling, red-fruit character, bright acid. The sparkle cuts the cream and the rosé plays against the tomato-paste component in the rebuild. Non-obvious sparkling pour with real logic.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Reposado Tequila": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this reposado tequila's oak-kissed agave with vanilla and medium weight. Reposado + oak-kissed intersects with creamy + seafood — the pairing lands on weight and flavor alignment. A strong match — the register aligns cleanly.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Sanford & Benedict Pinot Noir": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this elegant red's cherry-bright, silky-tannin frame. The elegant red's cherry and earth anchor into rich soup depth — acidity cuts the cream. Strong — bright fruit lifts the weight.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Sauternes Glass": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets the Sauternes' botrytised honey, stone-fruit, and apricot sweetness. Port-style sweetness isn't built to sit with savory plates; the sugar takes over. Strong bridge pour when the dish leans sweet-savory.",
  "Shrimp Bisque|Sazerac": "Shrimp Bisque: this rich, creamy seafood soup's sweet-briny depth over dairy-rich base meets this bold whiskey-forward cocktail's oak, spice, and spirit depth. Cocktail against a creamy seafood soup — acidity and lift cut the dairy base while the spirit carries its own weight. Works cleanly.",
