  "Shrimp Cocktail|The Happy Wife": "Tito's with orange juice and ginger syrup, stirred with a brûléed orange garnish. The OJ's sweetness balances the cocktail sauce's horseradish heat; the ginger adds warmth. Approachable pour for a guest who wants something easy.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|The Prisoner Red Blend": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Delicate seafood or mild creams buckle under the bold red's tannin. Avoid — register mismatch.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Transfusion": "Hangar 1 vodka muddled with black grapes and lime, topped with ginger beer. The grape fruit and ginger-beer effervescence keep the drink light enough for cold shrimp. More complex than it looks; honest fit.",
  "Shrimp Cocktail|Venge Family Reserve": "Shrimp Cocktail: this delicate seafood starter's briny-fresh sweetness meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. Delicate seafood or mild creams buckle under the bold red's tannin. Avoid — register mismatch.",
