  "Spiced / Flavored Rum|Beignets": "Spiced / Flavored Rum: this spiced rum's sweet, approachable warmth meets the beignets' light, airy, powdered-sugar sweetness. Spiced + sweet intersects with fried + light — the pairing lands on weight and flavor alignment. A headliner pair — both elements show at their best.",
