  "St Supéry Cabernet Sauvignon|Kansas City": "St Supéry — Napa Rutherford Cab with blackberry, cassis, mocha, firm tannin. The full body meets Kansas City's lean-bold marbled strip and the firm tannin frames the beefy char. Peak by-the-glass Napa Cab for Kansas City — accessible price point for a classic steak-and-Cab pairing.",
  "St Supéry Cabernet Sauvignon|Mushrooms": "Napa Rutherford Cab — blackberry, cassis, mocha, full body. The earth-mocha profile meshes directly with mushroom umami and the firm tannin frames the sauté without overwhelming. Peak by-the-glass Cab for mushrooms — classic Napa character, natural earth-on-earth pairing.",
